      • getWorkspaceFile

        @GET(value="v2/accounts/{accountId}/workspaces/{workspaceId}/folders/{folderId}/files/{fileId}")
retrofit2.Call<Void> getWorkspaceFile(@Path(value="accountId")
                                                                                                                                       String accountId,
                                                                                                                                       @Path(value="fileId")
                                                                                                                                       String fileId,
                                                                                                                                       @Path(value="folderId")
                                                                                                                                       String folderId,
                                                                                                                                       @Path(value="workspaceId")
                                                                                                                                       String workspaceId,
                                                                                                                                       @Query(value="is_download")
                                                                                                                                       String isDownload,
                                                                                                                                       @Query(value="pdf_version")
                                                                                                                                       String pdfVersion)
        Get Workspace File Retrieves a workspace file (the binary).
        Parameters:
        accountId - The external account number (int) or account ID Guid. (required)
        fileId - Specifies the room file ID GUID. (required)
        folderId - The ID of the folder being accessed. (required)
        workspaceId - Specifies the workspace ID GUID. (required)
        isDownload - When set to **true**, the Content-Disposition header is set in the response. The value of the header provides the filename of the file. Default is **false**. (optional)
        pdfVersion - When set to **true** the file returned as a PDF. (optional)
        Returns:
        Call

      • listWorkspaceFilePages

        @GET(value="v2/accounts/{accountId}/workspaces/{workspaceId}/folders/{folderId}/files/{fileId}/pages")
retrofit2.Call<PageImages> listWorkspaceFilePages(@Path(value="accountId")
                                                                                                                                                         String accountId,
                                                                                                                                                         @Path(value="fileId")
                                                                                                                                                         String fileId,
                                                                                                                                                         @Path(value="folderId")
                                                                                                                                                         String folderId,
                                                                                                                                                         @Path(value="workspaceId")
                                                                                                                                                         String workspaceId,
                                                                                                                                                         @Query(value="count")
                                                                                                                                                         String count,
                                                                                                                                                         @Query(value="dpi")
                                                                                                                                                         String dpi,
                                                                                                                                                         @Query(value="max_height")
                                                                                                                                                         String maxHeight,
                                                                                                                                                         @Query(value="max_width")
                                                                                                                                                         String maxWidth,
                                                                                                                                                         @Query(value="start_position")
                                                                                                                                                         String startPosition)
        List File Pages Retrieves a workspace file as rasterized pages.
        Parameters:
        accountId - The external account number (int) or account ID Guid. (required)
        fileId - Specifies the room file ID GUID. (required)
        folderId - The ID of the folder being accessed. (required)
        workspaceId - Specifies the workspace ID GUID. (required)
        count - The maximum number of results to be returned by this request. (optional)
        dpi - Number of dots per inch for the resulting image. The default if not used is 94. The range is 1-310. (optional)
        maxHeight - Sets the maximum height (in pixels) of the returned image. (optional)
        maxWidth - Sets the maximum width (in pixels) of the returned image. (optional)
        startPosition - The position within the total result set from which to start returning values. The value **thumbnail** may be used to return the page image. (optional)
        Returns:
        Call

      • listWorkspaceFolderItems

        @GET(value="v2/accounts/{accountId}/workspaces/{workspaceId}/folders/{folderId}")
retrofit2.Call<WorkspaceFolderContents> listWorkspaceFolderItems(@Path(value="accountId")
                                                                                                                                                   String accountId,
                                                                                                                                                   @Path(value="folderId")
                                                                                                                                                   String folderId,
                                                                                                                                                   @Path(value="workspaceId")
                                                                                                                                                   String workspaceId,
                                                                                                                                                   @Query(value="count")
                                                                                                                                                   String count,
                                                                                                                                                   @Query(value="include_files")
                                                                                                                                                   String includeFiles,
                                                                                                                                                   @Query(value="include_sub_folders")
                                                                                                                                                   String includeSubFolders,
                                                                                                                                                   @Query(value="include_thumbnails")
                                                                                                                                                   String includeThumbnails,
                                                                                                                                                   @Query(value="include_user_detail")
                                                                                                                                                   String includeUserDetail,
                                                                                                                                                   @Query(value="start_position")
                                                                                                                                                   String startPosition,
                                                                                                                                                   @Query(value="workspace_user_id")
                                                                                                                                                   String workspaceUserId)
        List Workspace Folder Contents Retrieves workspace folder contents, which can include sub folders and files.
        Parameters:
        accountId - The external account number (int) or account ID Guid. (required)
        folderId - The ID of the folder being accessed. (required)
        workspaceId - Specifies the workspace ID GUID. (required)
        count - The maximum number of results to be returned by this request. (optional)
        includeFiles - When set to **true**, file information is returned in the response along with folder information. The default is **false**. (optional)
        includeSubFolders - When set to **true**, information about the sub-folders of the current folder is returned. The default is **false**. (optional)
        includeThumbnails - When set to **true**, thumbnails are returned as part of the response. The default is **false**. (optional)
        includeUserDetail - Set to **true** to return extended details about the user. The default is **false**. (optional)
        startPosition - The position within the total result set from which to start returning values. (optional)
        workspaceUserId - If set, then the results are filtered to those associated with the specified userId. (optional)
        Returns:
        Call
